xorg-sgml-doctools (1:1.7-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
    - Add support for docbook external references.
  * Update .install file accordingly for new XML/XSL files.
  * Bump xutils-dev build-dep for new macros.
  * Update Uploaders list. Thanks, David!
  * Switch to dh:
    - Bump compat to 8.
    - Use dh-autoreconf.
    - Use quilt (so that we're ready to patch if needed).
    - Pass --fail-missing to dh_install for additional safety.
  * Get rid of (removed) --enable-man-pages configure flag.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 3.9.1 (no changes needed).

